{"id":29486,"date":"2024-02-28T07:32:00","date_gmt":"2021-12-28T02:02:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=29486"},"modified":"2024-11-28T15:42:17","modified_gmt":"2024-11-28T10:12:17","slug":"design-cafe-modular-furniture-benefits","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/dc-updates\/design-cafe-modular-furniture-benefits\/","title":{"rendered":"Find Out What Makes DesignCafe Modular Furniture Special"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Home is where your heart lies, so design it exactly the way your heart desires<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The most beautiful haven in this world is home. It is not just a concrete structure made of walls, it&#8217;s an emotion, a feeling, a nest that we all want to get back to. It is a place of comfort where you can be yourself, your small universe where every corner resonates with you. And one of the most crucial things that help you transform a house into your home is the interiors. Decor, modular furniture and everything that makes that dream home a reality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trusting someone with such a big responsibility can be a little daunting, but we at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a>, value your emotions. It is our greatest goal to transform your house into the home that you have always dreamt of. DesignCafe\u2019s modular furniture speaks for itself. The durability, finish, texture, quality and modern mechanisms are perfect for making your home look elegant, efficient and functional, and exactly how you want your home to be!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Let&#8217;s Get To Know What Is Modular Furniture<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Modular furniture, unlike carpentered furniture, is a set of furniture items that can be tailored to your home and requirements. It renders a sleek finish and provides ample storage space for your home. It helps you access the corners and dead ends and use them for storage purposes that would otherwise be impossible. Modular furniture can also be disassembled and assembled as per your needs. Modular furniture for the home is durable, sustainable, easily replaceable and gives you the liberty to experiment with modern textures, finishes and mechanisms that lend a luxurious feel to your home and improve efficiency.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144421\/what-is-modular-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"What is modular furniture\" class=\"wp-image-29495\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144421\/what-is-modular-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144421\/what-is-modular-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144421\/what-is-modular-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144421\/what-is-modular-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Modular furniture is all about efficiency with aesthetics<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Modular Furniture Design Ensures Maximum Space And Efficiency In The Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The kitchen is one of the most essential parts of any household. Modern designs and technology assure 20 per cent more storage space in your kitchen. With ultra-modern technologies like skirting drawers, appliance garage, magic corner units, tandem drawers, janitor units, S and D-shaped carousels, pull-out drawers and under-sink units, every corner of your kitchen is utilised and you enjoy a clutter-free cooking experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144648\/design-cafes-modular-kitchen-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"DesignCafe's modular kitchen furniture ensures space-maximising and efficiency\" class=\"wp-image-29496\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144648\/design-cafes-modular-kitchen-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144648\/design-cafes-modular-kitchen-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144648\/design-cafes-modular-kitchen-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144648\/design-cafes-modular-kitchen-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">We are proud of our ultra-modern and space-maximising modular kitchen furniture<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Increase Efficiency And Utility With Modern Modular Furniture For Your Home<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our living and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom interiors<\/a> are equally efficient and elegant. All our modular furniture designs are made using high-quality material and laminates that are water-resistant, durable, sustainable and improve your home&#8217;s efficiency. The foldable cabinets, TV units and wardrobes provide ample storage options and help you keep your space organised and clutter-free. You can check out our blog and guide section to understand more about our range of modular furniture for the home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144836\/design-cafes-modular-furniture-design.jpg\" alt=\"DesignCafe offers modular bed furniture that promotes efficiency and a clutter-free living space\" class=\"wp-image-29497\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144836\/design-cafes-modular-furniture-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144836\/design-cafes-modular-furniture-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144836\/design-cafes-modular-furniture-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144836\/design-cafes-modular-furniture-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Our modular furniture design helps your keep your space clean and clutter-free<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What&#8217;s Special About DesignCafe&#8217;s Modular Furniture<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We make sure everything that goes into crafting our modular furniture design is of the highest quality. For dry areas, we use High-Density Fibreboard, and for the wet areas of the home, we use Boiling Water Proof (BWP) plywood, Hydro-Density and High Moisture Resistant (HYDMR) plywood. All of these are ISI certified. Our German-finished imported laminates are the best in the industry.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We know how annoying it gets to see furniture with jagged edges, banging cabinet drawers or rusting hinges. But the quality of our modular furniture for home and our customer\u2019s satisfaction is DesignCafe\u2019s prime focus. Our factory-finished modular furniture gives you ultra-smooth finishing with baby-proofing benefits. They are water-resistant and keep your home safe from fungus and bacteria as well. Even the hinges, handles and panels are made of premium quality to avoid rusting or decay.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144937\/whats-special-about-design-cafes-modular-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"DesignCafe always ensures the highest quality standards are met regarding modular furniture and never compromises on them\" class=\"wp-image-29498\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144937\/whats-special-about-design-cafes-modular-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144937\/whats-special-about-design-cafes-modular-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144937\/whats-special-about-design-cafes-modular-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144937\/whats-special-about-design-cafes-modular-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">We never compromise on the quality of our products<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Designers And Happiness Managers Make The Process Easy And Hassle-free<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We are committed to transforming your house into your dream home. Our designers and Happiness Managers work with you to understand your needs, style preference and budget to give you the best. Incorporating space-saving modular furniture in home interiors is one of our USPs, but we also try to personalise your space for you. Be it an indoor garden, meditation room, gaming room, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/small-pooja-room-designs-in-apartments\/\">small puja room<\/a>, spiral stairs, a playful kids room or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/home-office-design\/\">home office<\/a>, our top-notch designers try to customise the design to give you everything your heart desires.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144408\/process-of-design-cafes-modular-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"DesignCafe's designer and happiness manager make the modular furniture design process easy and hassle-free\" class=\"wp-image-29493\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144408\/process-of-design-cafes-modular-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144408\/process-of-design-cafes-modular-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144408\/process-of-design-cafes-modular-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144408\/process-of-design-cafes-modular-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Our designers will help you throughout the process of upgrading your home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Service Comes With A 10-Year Warranty And Free Maintenance<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We ensure to provide you with the best quality interiors that are cost-effective and suit your taste. Before the installation, every product goes through 51 stringent quality checks and our trained staff makes sure that your floor remains intact during installation. We are proud of our on-time delivery that is taken care of by our efficient project managers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our service comes with ten years of warranty and free maintenance, so if you sign up with DesignCafe you will get your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">home interiors<\/a> done in an easy, hassle-free manner with the best modular furniture.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144402\/design-cafes-modular-furniture-service.jpg\" alt=\"DesignCafe offers a ten-year warranty and free maintenance services for their modular furniture for home\" class=\"wp-image-29492\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144402\/design-cafes-modular-furniture-service.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144402\/design-cafes-modular-furniture-service-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144402\/design-cafes-modular-furniture-service-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/27144402\/design-cafes-modular-furniture-service-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">We provide 10 years of warranty and free maintenance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So if you want a home that has all these modern features, equipped with the latest modular furniture along with your personal touch, do get a free consultation with our designers. You can also walk into any of our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/experience-centre\/\">experience centres<\/a> to get a better idea of our designs. And for more such bogs, do check our blog section.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Tailored Interiors That Reflect Your Style<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get end-to-end interior design solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n     